  "author": "Guru Bin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The Shepard reverb — shimmer feedback at 0.85 with octave shift at 0.8 creates a reverb tail that perpetually ascends. Each reflection feeds back through the pitch-up processor, constructing an infinite staircase of light. You play a note and it climbs forever. The ceiling does not exist. This is Aurum's revelation, fully committed: the moment shimmer feedback crosses 0.80, the decay becomes a direction rather than a diminishment.",
  "tags": ["opensky", "infinite", "shimmer", "transcendent", "aether", "guru-bin", "shepard", "ascension"],
  "tier": "transcendental",
  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OPENSKY — Above the Cloud Line",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "vol": "Transcendental Vol 1",
    "scripture": [
      "Verse 5: Shepard Shimmer — The Reverb That Never Descends",
      "Gospel 1: This Is the Sound of Looking Up and Never Finding the Ceiling",
      "Discovery 2: Shimmer Spectrum — feedback 0.80-0.85 enters the INFINITE zone, a Shepard scale reverb"
    ],
    "revelation": "Aurum's Revelation: above feedback=0.80, the reverb tail becomes a direction, not a duration",
    "god": null,
    "flock_note": "The Ear followed the shimmer into the stratosphere — the tail climbed without stopping. The Eye watched the spectrum analyzer confirm infinite ascent. Play any note and release it. Wait. The sound does not die; it continues upward until you can no longer hear it, replaced by a new layer climbing behind it.",
    "diagnosis": "Infinite Rise is the OPENSKY transcendence preset — shimmer feedback at the Shepard threshold (0.85) with strong octave shift creates a feedback loop that continually climbs. The physiological LFO at 0.067 Hz adds one barely-perceptible breath over fifteen seconds. Reserve this for moments requiring spiritual altitude."
  },
